Testcase:2 (Amazon)
==========
01) Launch Firefox / Chrome / Safari / Edge  
02) Load https://www.amazon.in/
  Add  implicitlyWait -  driver.manage().timeouts().implicitlyWait(Duration.ofSeconds(30));
03) Click "Mobiles"
04) Click "Smartphones & Basic Mobiles"
05) Select "128GB" from checkbox
06) Click "See more" link from Brands and select "POCO"
07) Print the first filtered mobile details and click on it
08) Print the title of the webpage
09) Take a screenshot of the product
10) Click the "Add To Cart" button
11) Close the browser